"""Test update_storage_group_qos exception."""
storage_group_name = self.create_empty_storage_group()
qos_update = {constants.MAX_MBPS: '3000', constants.DISTRIBUTION_TYPE:
    'Invalid Type'}
self.assertRaises(exception.InvalidInputException, self.provisioning.
    update_storage_group_qos, storage_group_name, qos_update)
